---
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from "../config";
---

<section id="contact" class="section section-alt">
  <div class="shell">
    <h2 class="section-title">Contact &amp; bookings</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Ready to ride, or just want to understand what’s possible for your dates
      and level? Send a short message with:
    </p>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li>Dates you are in the area</li>
      <li>Number of riders &amp; approximate level</li>
      <li>MTB or e-MTB, and if you need rental</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="contact-box">
      <p>Email:</p>
      <p class="contact-main">
        <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
      </p>
      <p class="contact-note">
        You can write in English or Italian. We’ll reply with options,
        difficulty, and a clear price for your group.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
